ExecDesc.value: ClamAV libclamav PE File Handling Integer Overflow (IPv6 Version)

EngDesc.value: A buffer overflow vulnerability exists in the ClamAV AntiVirus product. The vulnerability can be triggered when the application processes crafted PE files. An unauthenticated attacker can exploit this vulnerability by delivering a crafted file to the scanning service resulting in injection and execution of arbitrary code. (IPv6 Version)
